3. HOW WE USE INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

We use the information we collect to:
  - Provide, operate, and maintain the Service and your account;
  - Match shippers, carriers, and dispatchers, and facilitate the posting,
    booking, assignment, and management of loads and shipments;
  - Enable real-time delivery tracking and route/map functionality;
  - Enable in-app messaging, including on-demand translation of messages into
    your selected interface language;
  - Send transactional and operational notifications;
  - Process and display proof-of-delivery and other documents;
  - Provide ratings and reputation features;
  - Maintain the security, integrity, and reliability of the Service, and
    prevent fraud and abuse;
  - Comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. HOW INFORMATION IS SHARED
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

We share information only as needed to operate the Service:

  - With other users on the platform: when you participate in a shipment, the
    relevant parties (shipper, carrier, dispatcher, and assigned driver) can
    see information needed to complete the work — for example your name and
    contact details, the shipment details, chat messages, shared locations,
    proof-of-delivery, and, during an active assigned delivery, your live
    location.

  - With service providers: we use trusted third parties to provide
    infrastructure and features, including:
      * Google Firebase Cloud Messaging — push notifications;
      * Map, geocoding, and routing services accessed through our backend;
      * Cloud hosting and storage for the App's data, documents, and images.
    These providers process information on our behalf under appropriate
    obligations.

  - For legal reasons: we may disclose information if required by law, legal
    process, or to protect the rights, safety, and security of our users,
    the public, or the Company.

  - Business transfers: if the Company is involved in a merger, acquisition,
    or sale of assets, information may be transferred as part of that
    transaction, subject to this Policy.

  We do not sell your personal information.

